rooms.Name: Aboard the Chaos ship.
rooms.Description:
Flashing yellow lights line this corridor accompanied by loud sirens. Bulkheads
can be seen above you scared and seared as if a huge battle took place here.
Cold air blasts your face as it streams out of a busted pipe. Small port holes
let you look out into the high atomsphere of Macragge.

rooms.Name: Aboard the Chaos ship.
rooms.Description:
Flashing yellow lights line this corridor accompanied by loud sirens. Yellow
caution stripes can be seen on the walls with hoses and tubes. Cold air blasts
your face as it streams out of a busted pipe. Steel grates line the floor,
some like as if they have been eaten through by acid.

rooms.Name: Aboard the Chaos ship.
rooms.Description:
Flashing yellow lights line this corridor accompanied by loud sirens. Busted
hoses and pipes spray steam and smoke into the room. The air in this room is
so thin you can hardly breathe. Bodies of Imperial space marines lay strewn
across the floor.

rooms.Description:

faces and pagan carvings can be seen on all the walls in this room. The air
here smells like sulfur and your eyes can not stop from watering. Bodies of
Imperial space marines lay strewn across the floor.
